Class AbstractSvtEvioReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.evio.EvioReader
      • org.hps.evio.AbstractSvtEvioReader
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseSvtEvioReader, Phys2019SvtEvioReader, SvtEvioReader

    public abstract class AbstractSvtEvioReader
extends EvioReader
    Abstract SVT EVIO reader used to convert SVT bank sample blocks to RawTrackerHits.
